com.viaoa.web

Class OACheckBox

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.web.OACheckBox
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, OAJspRequirementsInterface, OATableEditor, ComponentInterface, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OARadio

    public class OACheckBox
extends Object
implements OAJspComponent, OATableEditor, OAJspRequirementsInterface, ComponentInterface
    Controls an html input type=checkbox bind to hub, property show/hide, that can be bound to property enabled, that can be bound to property ajax submit on change
    Author:
    vvia

    Serialized Form
